{"tid":1452030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「黑警」，試著說「老鼠屎」","createTime":"2019-08-11T23:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:08:56.000Z","uid":107717,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"065507f5cc9e303c85d5913a87ce60894b4f471b","tid":1452030,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:26:01.000Z","msg":"經過811屠殺事件<br />\n相信大家都唔會再信班popo老鼠屎會有良知所以決定開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家留意返 對家由7月中後已經開始叫我哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「曱甴」</span>（唔係好肯定，大概721元朗恐襲？）<br />\n例子：（立場圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/937SGxM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F937SGxM.png&h=93784855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係做緊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「去人性化」(Dehumanization)</span></span><br />\n簡單啲講即係潛移默化令popo覺得對住示威者做咩都合理 包括暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（同係屋企見到真曱甴會又打又噴殺蟲水同一道理）<br />\n呢套理論當年都係納粹德國對付過猶太人&amp;盧旺達屠殺（source：隔離post <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442391）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442391）</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但係曱甴生命力強而且係地球已經4億年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n點樣還擊呢 除咗宣傳popo用納粹手法對付示威者<br />\n我覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">名稱上</span>都可以升級<br />\n諗咗陣 決定以後唔叫popo 叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老鼠屎</span></span><br />\n點解唔叫恐怖分子？因為都係人類囉<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 諺語「<span style=\"color: teal;\">一粒老鼠屎 壞了一鍋粥</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    暗示你班popo &amp; 同夥先係搞臭香港嘅屎<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: teal;\">降低前線手足心理底線</span> 暗示popo唔係人<br />\n    曱甴至少係生物 你堆屎生物都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（呢個係雙刃劍 有可能會出事）<br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1. 可能會有<span style=\"color: teal;\">路西法效應</span>令民意抑制<br />\n    利申核彈都唔割 但係香港太多割蓆大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 對家又攞去做文章 <span style=\"color: teal;\">外媒可能都會報呢個名</span><br />\n上面好處有個雙刃劍嘅原因就係係度 因為我地都都係做返同一樣嘢「去人性化」 會唔會比外媒抹黑呢&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n利申 依然支持正名恐怖分子<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中国香港警察</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">恐怖份子</span>=<span style=\"color: blue;\">搞臭香港嘅老鼠屎</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3776433f5e8aec7e042a33f7224414ca1cb5e28","tid":1452030,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:26:45.000Z","msg":"老鼠屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa988b40ca6cabadd064d6223683e06eb98589be","tid":1452030,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:26:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1dbf223331474b443d3ff7091edd8f83026f2a63","tid":1452030,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:27:10.000Z","msg":"老鼠屎禍港"},{"pid":"29e809a210266891b728a45cd71c5ce2327c4140","tid":1452030,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:27:41.000Z","msg":"香港唔歡迎老鼠屎"},{"pid":"ae43f3970c21d9aa75cdcb2f8b4fb2803ae68436","tid":1452030,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:28:26.000Z","msg":"香港唔歡迎三萬老鼠屎及其親屬"},{"pid":"c102b0c2d30dcb5a7978d12e63e0f4a897cf6c10","tid":1452030,"uid":2757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:28:29.000Z","msg":"叫垃撚圾"},{"pid":"9a64e5f1e1723bb2c95c8a5639afa551eaf6a944","tid":1452030,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c102b0c2d30dcb5a7978d12e63e0f4a897cf6c10","tid":1452030,"uid":2757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:28:29.000Z","msg":"叫垃撚圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:29:15.000Z","msg":"不可回收嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4b7e4012d23d30225a2ecca20ddd0ebbc0b6c6","tid":1452030,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislik